SELECT
  *
FROM (
  SELECT
    score,
    DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL (ROW_NUMBER() OVER () - 1) DAY) AS zeit
  FROM UNNEST([0.5, 0.7, 0.2, 0.3, 0.5, 0.4, 0.9]) AS score
) AS dummy_data

targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  score[0],score[1]
FROM (
  SELECT
    score
  FROM UNNEST([(RAND()*1000,"Montag"), (RAND()*1000,"Dienstag"), (RAND()*1000,"Mittwoch"), (RAND()*1000,"Donnerstag"), (RAND()*1000,"Freitag"), (RAND()*1000,"Samstag"), (RAND()*1000,"Sonntag")]) AS score
) AS dummy_data

SELECT
  CAST(number AS STRING) AS zeit,
  ROUND(RAND() * 100) AS score
FROM
  UNNEST(GENERATE_ARRAY(1, 24)) AS number

SELECT
  CAST(number AS STRING) AS zeit,
  ROUND(RAND() * 1000) AS score
FROM
  UNNEST(GENERATE_ARRAY(1, 24)) AS number

SELECT
  *
FROM (
  SELECT
    score,
    DATE_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL (ROW_NUMBER() OVER () - 1) DAY) AS zeit
  FROM UNNEST(ARRAY_REVERSE(GENERATE_ARRAY(100000,120000,20000/6))) AS score
) AS dummy_data
